
xmcd - Full-featured CD player and ripper

by Ti Kan

Package includes:

xmcd - Motif-based CD player with CDDB interface
cda - command-line utility with curses-based, screen-oriented mode

Supports CD recognition via Gracenote CDDB (R). It can connect to the
CDDB servers on the Internet to get the artist, disc title, song
titles and other information about the CD you're playing.

Installation notes:

1) Run /usr/lib64/X11/xmcd/config.sh as root after installation to
   configure your CDROM device. Re-run as needed to try out
   different config settings.

2) FLAC support disabled in this Slackbuild

